<p>GDP growth: 3.6% GDP: $47bn (PPP: $62bn) Inflation: 3.3% Population: 4.3m GDP per head: $10,880 (PPP: $14,370)</p>

<p>As ever, external forces will drive internal developments in this battered country. Domestic forces aligned with Syria and Iran will remain in the ascendant, despite troubles facing the Syrian regime. The government must urgently address a structural fiscal deficit, chronic energy shortages and widespread corruption.</p>

